{#tIraniKAtayUpA vahatyayoDyAmanu rAjaDAnIM#}  
<ls>R. 13. 61</ls>; {#trisrotasaM vahati yo gaganapratizWAM#}
<ls>Ś. 7. 6</ls>; <ls>R. 11. 10.</ls>

{@--4@}
